  "text": "Now we describe the colour structure of the five-point, two-loop amplitude. We concentrate on the diagrams that do not vanish in the all-plus case according to ref. [CITATION_1] and our calculations in section 4. A generic five-point two-loop amplitude can be constructed by a straightforward extension of the present discussion.",
